\c 28
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi, achiti:
\v 2 Raira vana vaIsraeri ugoti kwavari: Chipo changu, chingwa changu chechipo chemoto\x + Rev. 3.11.\x*, hwema hunonhuhwira hwangu, muchachenjerera kupa kwandiri nenguva yacho yakatarwa.
\v 3 Zvino uchati kwavari: Ichi chipo chemoto chamuchapa kuna Jehovha\x + Eki. 29.38.\x*: Makwayana maviri egore rimwe, asina gwapa, zuva rimwe nerimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa nguva dzose.
\v 4 Rimwe gwayana ucharigadzira mangwanani, uye rimwe gwayana ucharigadzira madekwani;
\v 5 nechegumi cheefa yeupfu hwakatsetseka\x + Eki. 16.36. Num. 15.4.\x* chive chipo chechidyiwa\x + Rev. 2.1.\x*, hwakakanyiwa nechechina chehini yemafuta akasviniwa\x + Eki. 29.40.\x*.
\v 6 Chipo chinopiswa chenguva dzose\x + Eki. 29.42. Amo. 5.25.\x*, chakagadzwa pagomo reSinai kuva hwema hunonhuhwira, chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha.
\v 7 Nechipo chacho chezvinwiwa zvichava chechina chehini chegwayana rimwe; uchadururira Jehovha chipo chezvinwiwa zvinodhaka panzvimbo tsvene\x + Eki. 29.42.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino rimwe gwayana ucharigadzira madekwani; sechipo chechidyiwa chemangwanani uye sechipo chechinwiwa chacho uchazvipa, chipo chemoto chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 9 Uye nezuva resabata makwayana maviri egore rimwe, asina gwapa, nezvegumi zviviri zveupfu hwakatsetseka kuva chipo chechidyiwa, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, nechipo chacho chechinwiwa;
\v 10 chipo chinopiswa chesabata pasabata racho\x + Eze. 46.4,5.\x*, pamusoro pechipo chinopiswa nguva dzose, nechipo chacho chechinwiwa.
\p
\v 11 Zvino pakuvamba kwemwedzi yenyu muchapa chipo chinopiswa kuna Jehovha\x + 10.10. 1 Zvak. 20.5. 1 Makor. 23.31. 2 Makor. 2.4. Ezi. 3.5. Neh. 10.33. Isa. 1.13,14. Eze. 45.17. 46.6. Hos. 2.11. VaKoro. 2.16.\x*: Nzombe diki mhuru dzemombe mbiri, negondohwe rimwe, makwayana manomwe egore rimwe, asina gwapa;
\v 12 nezvegumi zvitatu zveupfu hwakatsetseka chive chipo chechidyiwa, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, panzombe diki imwe\x + 15.4-12.\x*; nezvegumi zviviri zveupfu hwakatsetseka chive chipo chechidyiwa, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, pagondohwe rimwe;
\v 13 uye ndeichi neichi chegumi cheupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, chive chipo chechidyiwa, pagwayana rimwe; chive chipo chinopiswa, hwema hunonhuhwira, chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha.
\v 14 Zvino zvipo zvazvo zvechinwiwa zvichava hafu yehini yewaini panzombe diki, nechetatu chehini pagondohwe, nechechina chehini pagwayana; ichi chipo chinopiswa chemwedzi mumwedzi wacho mumwedzi yose yegore.
\v 15 Uye mbudzana yembudzi imwe igadzirwe kuva chipo chezvivi kuna Jehovha\x + 28.30.15.24. 29.11,16,19,25,22.\x*, pamusoro pechipo chinopiswa chenguva dzose, nechipo chacho chechinwiwa.
\s Mitambo mikuru
\p
\v 16 Zvino pamwedzi wekutanga nezuva regumi nemana remwedzi ipasika kuna Jehovha\x + Eki. 12.6. Det. 16.1. Eze. 45.21.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino nezuva regumi nemashanu remwedzi uno uchava mutambo\x + Rev. 23.6. Eki. 12.18.\x*: Chingwa chisina kuviriswa chichadyiwa mazuva manomwe.
\v 18 Nezuva rekutanga kuchava neungano yakadanwa tsvene\x + Eki. 12.16. Rev. 23.7.\x*; musaita chero basa revaranda;
\v 19 asi muchapa chibairo chemoto, chipo chinopiswa kuna Jehovha: Nzombe diki mhuru dzemombe mbiri, negondohwe rimwe, nemakwayana manomwe egore rimwe, zvichava kwamuri zvisina chazvingapomerwa\x + 28.31. Rev. 22.20. Num. 29.8,13. Rev. 22.20. Num. 29.2,17,20,23,26,29,32,36. Det. 15.21. 17.1.\x*;
\v 20 nechipo chazvo chechidyiwa, upfu hwakatsetseka hwakakanyiwa nemafuta; muchapa nezvegumi zvitatu panzombe diki, nezvegumi zviviri pagondohwe.
\v 21 Icho neicho chegumi muchapa pagwayana rimwe, pamakwayana manomwe;
\v 22 nenhongo imwe chive chipo chezvivi, kukuitirai chiyananiso\x + 28.15,30. 29.22,28,31,34,38.\x*.
\v 23 Muchapa izvi kusingaverengwi chipo chinopiswa mangwanani chiri chechipo chinopiswa chenguva dzose.
\v 24 Nenzira iyi muchagadzira zuva rimwe nerimwe, mazuva manomwe\x + 28.3.\x*, chidyiwa chechipo chemoto, hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha; chichapiwa pamusoro pechipo chinopiswa nguva dzose, nechipo chacho chechinwiwa.
\v 25 Zvino pazuva rechinomwe muchava neungano yakadanwa tsvene\x + Eki. 12.16. Rev. 23.8. Eki. 13.6.\x*; musaita chero basa revaranda.
\p
\v 26 Uye nezuva rezvibereko zvekutanga\x + Eki. 23.16. 34.22. Rev. 23.10,15. Det. 16.10. Mab. 2.1.\x*, pamunouisa chipo chechidyiwa chitsva kuna Jehovha, pamavhiki enyu, muchava neungano yakadanwa tsvene; musaita chero basa revaranda.
\v 27 Asi muchapa chipo chinopiswa kuva hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha: Nzombe diki mhuru dzemombe mbiri, gondohwe rimwe, makwayana manomwe egore rimwe\x + Rev. 23.18,19.\x*;
\v 28 nechipo chazvo chechidyiwa cheupfu hwakatsetseka hwakakanyiwa nemafuta; zvegumi zvitatu panzombe diki imwe, zvegumi zviviri pagondohwe rimwe;
\v 29 icho neicho chegumi pagwayana rimwe, pamakwayana manomwe;
\v 30 mbudzana yembudzi imwe, kukuitirai chiyananiso\x + 28.15. 29.5. 28.22.\x*.
\v 31 Muchagadzira izvi kusingaverengwi chipo chinopiswa nguva dzese, nechipo chacho chechidyiwa; zvive zvisina gwapa kwamuri, nezvipo zvako zvechinwiwa\x + 28.19.\x*.
